{"tid":2498903,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★啟德發展區8日3宗奪命意外　男工遭石屎斗砸斃","createTime":"2021-04-21T13:05:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T13:12:31.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"61cabb3eba9c76a7e8639780371f5af9155bef39","tid":2498903,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T13:05:04.000Z","msg":"啟德發展區再有工業意外！今午(21日)4時許，一輛吊臂車於啟福道油站對開一地盤，吊起一個石屎斗進行工程時，吊臂車突然向左傾側，石屎斗跌落泥坑內。一名姓黃(43歲)男工人疑走避不及，慘遭石屎斗砸中身體，他頭破血流、右腳重傷應聲而倒，附近工友見他頃刻間變成血人，慌忙報警。<br />\n<br />\n救護員趕至現場，事主昏迷不醒，立即抬上救護車送院，沿途需要接受心外壓急救，惜抵院後證實不治，黃妻其後到醫院了解，驚悉噩耗顯得黯然神傷。警方正調查意外原因。勞工處指，接報後已即時派員到現場，現正就意外原因展開調查。<br />\n據悉，死者黃文超，與同齡姓林妻子，育有一名現年8歲的兒子，一家人居於牛頭角恆安街明輝大樓。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20210421/bkn-20210421172400082-0421_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20210421%2Fbkn-20210421172400082-0421_00822_001.html&d=Hmcjt6vcQR8GyvD5m8y4dD2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=094fcf2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20210421/bkn-20210421172400082-0421_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"095bb9f0ff9870a37b66bc207a93f1bd83aca7f0","tid":2498903,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T13:05:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nghost<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6f4f032a920238d4fb0809d985242a51b25adf7","tid":2498903,"uid":304431,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T13:06:31.000Z","msg":"今次會唔會又好爸爸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c760b42c70cf81ec1e96c8c357e0927405af877b","tid":2498903,"uid":1643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T13:07:38.000Z","msg":"又支那公司？又黑工？"},{"pid":"e0d1c1d585c057b527be123dc8151832b42574e4","tid":2498903,"uid":366457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e6f4f032a920238d4fb0809d985242a51b25adf7","tid":2498903,"uid":304431,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T13:06:31.000Z","msg":"今次會唔會又好爸爸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T13:12:09.000Z","msg":"會啦，死親都係娶支國婆嘅好爸爸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02bd935455d81183ef1473d3f276b7662e0e1995","tid":2498903,"uid":25794,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T13:12:31.000Z","msg":"好爸爸+1"}]}